{"tid":55536,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[這地球若果有柒頭] 南美爛尾遊記","createTime":"2016-12-26T13:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T10:39:43.000Z","uid":66954,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20a80649e6cdb9f8a8b93a10e42e8051f37e7d06","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"話說N年前我仲係一個終日榴槤旅遊blog既毒撚 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoNRk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoNRk.gif&h=ce1289f4&s={SIZE}\" />&nbsp;第一次見到天空之鏡既相，震撼到我呢未見過世面、未衝出過亞洲既毒撚小心靈，從果日開始salar de uyuni就成為咗我既dream place<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時間一年一年咁過去，日日得個諗字，2012年，說好的末日呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 世界竟然沒有末日對毒撚深受打擊! 就喺果一年毒撚做咗廢青，背起背囊出走兩個半月! 第一次流浪，第一次住青旅，第一次坐夜火車，第一次感受野外解放，第一次同剛認識既人結伴! 目標係世上另一個天堂之境 - 西藏!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n好似好型咁，但毒撚最忌有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;第一日就miss咗班機，媽，好柒呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 第一次坐長途巴，成8個鐘唔知點算心慌慌 (宜家我笑而不語)，唔敢講自己係香港人扮係廣東人驚比人昆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; 第一次住mix dorm攬住d錢訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自從做咗一次backpacker，當你眼界開咗 (dd)，你已返唔到轉頭，短線遊已經滿足唔到你，果種要探索世界，又要驚又要睇既慾望蠢蠢欲動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算你曾經幾型幾瀟灑都好，返到香港呢個毒氣室，你仍然乖乖變返個毒撚柒頭! 仍然日日望住人哋d相發夢。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一首春青的詩都會老，時間多恐怖&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉眼間又2015，時間過得真係好快，小毒撚都變老廢，唔知喺邊聽到句 &ldquo;心動，不如行動!&rdquo; 係囉，都心動咗幾廿年咯，宜家唔去等幾時呀? 當你下定咗決心，果種衝勁真係擋都擋唔住! (就好搞肚痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 連一個人睇戲都未試過既小毒撚，今次要單拖出走了，就要去南美搵我既dream place&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;"},{"pid":"f99bf6e1ffd44186686472f24df26a4ef5323e1d","tid":55536,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a575be14eaf08c968456cdd3eb272dc1604e17","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"廢話講夠，說時遲，那時快，我已經坐咗十幾個鐘亡命夜巴，由玻利維亞既首都la paz到咗Uyuni! 一跳落車我並無興奮地開心跳起yeah，因為我仲擔心緊到步先搵住宿既個抉擇係咪傻豬豬咗。。明明我不嬲都會喺早兩日book定hostel，偏偏來到行程最重要一站先黎發神經玩自己一獲!&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最衰之前比喺秘魯識既泡菜仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;恥笑我住埋d貴又遠既hostel，佢哋到步先搵都住得好過我! 又恥笑我買貴咗車飛，每次同佢哋鬥平都輸! 心有不甘，想要威返次 (比自己睇)，亦暗暗擔心會唔會又柒多穫。。<br />\n<br />\n朝早7點天啱啱光天寒地凍，要喺凍死之前搵到地方落腳，鳩行人影都無，一齊落車d人都唔知死哂去邊。南美人咁鬼懶，神咁早都唔知起身未，好明顯就係未，終於搵到間hostel，落哂閘又無得㩒鐘仔，懷著又驚嘈到隔離，又驚嘈唔醒裡面既心情，當道門係殺父仇人咁喪拍!! 啪啪啪 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9Ou16.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9Ou16.gif&h=7e79c256&s={SIZE}\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;終於成功擾腦細清夢，你既犧牲係值得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;咁我就唔洗淪落街頭，仲以一個床位既價錢霸咗成間6人房，即刻撻落床訓覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n訓到中午起身喺hostel行咗轉覺得自己中咗伏! 有兩個公用廁所浴室，燈壞門壞，每次入去不安的心情就湧現，豎起耳仔聽下有無腳步聲接近 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &nbsp;個wifi勁弱，明明連咗線但上唔到網，同腦細反映竟然同我講，全個鎮都係用唔到wifi!! 吹脹。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n..感謝google提供照片<br />\n<img src=\"http://dts4h52y4acn7.cloudfront.net/2522364365411010943FBBEC59084B46f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdts4h52y4acn7.cloudfront.net%2F2522364365411010943FBBEC59084B46f.png&h=a90899b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出去搵旅行社，有做功課都知有兩間最出名，一間叫hodaka一間叫brisa兩間喺隔離左右，12點幾去到竟然關咗門! 原來呢興中場休息12點至3點唔開門! 如網上攻略所講，自己喺門口拼團紙仔寫名，3點開團返去旅行社睇下成唔成團，見hodaka成團機會大d我就即刻寫咗個大名喺下午sunset tour同今晚sunrise tour。想搵野食，點知餐廳都中場休息，得返做遊客生意餐廳有開，但窮撚無錢食。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n差唔多3點返去d架仔架妹已經喺門口等，見張紙仔都寫滿7個人名即係成團啦! 終於等佢開門比錢，分左兩團人出發，仲撞返之前秘魯遇過既韓妹，不過佢分咗去另一架車，我架車有日本，台灣，香港，大陸，清一式亞洲人。"},{"pid":"7109c5592c062850cdca4eb6db1b37ef2b209f90","tid":55536,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"樓主打咁大段野都未入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名 多圖多女唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d402b5f36fe0ff8d53e0409a4e2c8e33dcda4a0","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:17:43.000Z","msg":"懷住興奮既心情出發! 開咗10分鐘就停咗，原來要換水鞋先! 第一站竟然帶咗我哋去market，點呀，我黎睇天空之鏡呀! 留咗陣見我哋班人無幫襯又上路，今次黎咗呢個插滿旗既地方，都叫做必遊既景點既。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303248_31595343622_o_zpsoksbbnyu.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303248_31595343622_o_zpsoksbbnyu.jpg%20&h=d747539a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我要睇水呀鏡呀! 咪釣我癮ok? 終於入到鹽田上奔馳，一望無際，但仲未見到水，天空之鏡你喺邊呀!?&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303236%20Small_zpsw3cxy7fq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303236%2520Small_zpsw3cxy7fq.jpg&h=1178a05f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又停低咗睇一堆堆鹽山，有個架仔竟然想喺鹽堆解放 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp; &nbsp;比司機阻止咗，大佬呀，呢度如此雪白純潔，你個變態佬竟然想當眾污染佢，日本人的羞恥心呢?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303233%20Small_zpszligxur2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303233%2520Small_zpszligxur2.jpg&h=d2a76ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終於唔知吽咗幾耐，又繼續上路，同團有人剛剛去完day tour，呢d景佢今日先睇咗轉。點呀，又停咗喺一個完全無觀賞價值既地點，地下有幾個泉眼咁，又唔係靚又唔係熱，又唔係可以飲連浸腳都唔係，走啦，我求你，我要睇天空之鏡呀! 我跪你好無，唔好再折磨我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;(全部內心戲)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303239%20Small_zpsr8z22vfj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303239%2520Small_zpsr8z22vfj.jpg&h=28671269&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee726365bf618eaee9b95c80552912f5768a0ab6","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主打咁大段野都未入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名 多圖多女唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗咗幾晚，比比面睇兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb401bd01e72b376002245ddcfc4bcfa16dbc1bd","tid":55536,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主打咁大段野都未入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名 多圖多女唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗咗幾晚，比比面睇兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打經美國去定歐洲？"},{"pid":"9e2cf592a3e9b2001e744b1e6dd9984c20a3fcf9","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"當我哋再度上路，個天已經開始日落，我心裡無明火起! 毒撚都有火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;我一心黎睇天空之鏡，欣賞佢天光到日落直至天黑的顏色變化! 多角度慢慢陶醉，毒撚鼓起勇氣走出房門，山長水遠黎呢度，宜家日落緊都未見到水，好嬲呀好嬲呀! 但毒撚淨係夠膽心裡面暗嬲，至多喺面上擺出一絲不滿的表情 (根本無人望過一眼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &nbsp;)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/30900375294_865acd2ca6_z_zpsxm1dockj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F30900375294_865acd2ca6_z_zpsxm1dockj.jpg&h=fa510153&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但當眼前開始見到水，真正既天空之鏡出現喺我面前，逐步迫近，直至將我重重包圍，我已經唔識嬲，呆咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;然後同成班人一齊鳩叫! 跳落車，好似小朋友咁興奮，360自轉去睇清呢個我期待已久既畫面，如果有人望我一眼，就會見到我華麗轉身，身邊水花四濺，背景夢幻，直情好似sailor moon變身咁 (不過有著衫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無褲)，有人幫我影底就好鳥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303380_31369110480_o_zps5ahjejck.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303380_31369110480_o_zps5ahjejck.jpg&h=d4b03de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303285_30900571844_o_zps2den1o6p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303285_30900571844_o_zps2den1o6p.jpg&h=54e98a41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我哋來到的時間太遲，好快太陽已落山消失咗喺地平線之下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303424_31742265995_o_zps7fs4keaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303424_31742265995_o_zps7fs4keaa.jpg&h=24cd9a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲住杯熱茶，望住開始黑既天，星星出現，又另一翻景象! 不過氣溫急降，帶住依依不捨既心情離開。5個鐘既行程就此完結。返到hostel差唔多夜晚9點，凌晨3點又要出發去sunrise tour，但想即刻send相比家人朋友睇，但wifi又廢到無倫。。都係眠一眠好過。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303431%20Small_zps7nehj3bm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303431%2520Small_zps7nehj3bm.jpg&h=22c39c7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12a7c5014a989de1546d2bee2e14128e2300da6d","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"執完相再up, 之後開始無字得圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b575b8d594e4121af31a23d0c246d2942299125f","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T13:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主打咁大段野都未入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名 多圖多女唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n諗咗幾晚，比比面睇兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打經美國去定歐洲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歐洲，無美簽"},{"pid":"984a93d2fe8fd89878c1c9e5a7b8045ce020e361","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:07:25.000Z","msg":"凌晨2點幾起身，落到樓下大門又鎖咗!!! 出唔到去被人禁固呀救命，喺我唔知點算好既時候，老闆又出來了，唉，喺呢度經營旅館真係慘，成日無教好訓。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於日頭已經有人忠告我會撚凍到仆街，本來我都叫挨得凍，但比人凶一凶即刻淆底，喺背囊底拎返件羽絨出黎著，對上一次著佢係零下廿度，我係好憎羽絨，唔係會凍到死我都唔想著佢。最後我好興幸著咗佢出黎，真係凍撚到震唔停，加上我得返一隻孤獨的手套，另一隻手差d變紫色。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係好佩服個司機，黑到咩都見唔到，喺咁空擴分唔到東南西北，入到水連天同地都分唔到既地方都認得路! 當我一落車，望住天上既銀河，無數既星星，同反射喺鹽湖既鏡面，果種震撼勁過日頭一萬倍!!! 連聲都出唔到，大家都好靜，比眼前景象嚇傻左了。。。我係咪發緊夢呀? 肉眼睇銀河既感覺實在太奇妙太正喇!!! 同車的架仔韓妹好快就頂唔住好狠凍冷返上車，得返我同另一對台灣couple影相，由於我唔係好識影星，又無腳架，只可以放喺膠櫈度9影，無邊張影得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303477_31742239025_o_zpsg2qqbwqd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303477_31742239025_o_zpsg2qqbwqd.jpg&h=f59011fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303483_31369051640_o_zpskffig9ns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303483_31369051640_o_zpskffig9ns.jpg&h=02ca1f74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過好彩台灣couple好好人幫我影咗幾張，開心! 想請佢哋食凍柑&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/14304515223162.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F14304515223162.jpg&h=bf3bbc9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想好好珍惜眼前畫面，喺外面無上過車，即使已經冷到流哂鼻水<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nf8ze.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnf8ze.gif&h=96a13540&s={SIZE}\" />&nbsp;一秒都唔想浪費，眨眼都睇少0.0001秒! 今晚係我人生見過最多流星既一晚，多到諗唔到願望許願了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/31742232905_40f1043a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F31742232905_40f1043a0f.jpg&h=a720ad5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直到天開始光架仔韓妹就再次出動瘋狂自拍，係啱架，一場來到，唔拍個天荒地老點對得起自己，唔掙幫我拍幾張嘛。。見唔到我唔望鏡頭望遠方的文青沈思pose咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303547%20Small_zpstfvyczry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303547%2520Small_zpstfvyczry.jpg&h=d205737f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303551_31704487776_o_zpsh8tccueo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303551_31704487776_o_zpsh8tccueo.jpg&h=70440cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我曾經諗自己會唔會感動到喊，係無嘅! 當時的確開心、感動、興奮! 宜家諗返起都嘴角含春咁，但又未至於令我流出眼淚，太作狀了 (毒撚連喊都唔敢，最多柒到喊)&nbsp;"},{"pid":"90a2b568bc5479728fc30ae63c95eb13daec4136","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:21:05.000Z","msg":"太愛天空之鏡了，第2日我又join左brisa既sunset tour，直情想無限loop sunset sunrise tour直至精盡人亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;不過我仲有理志，唔係野獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;仲識得控制自己。喺我墮入呢個輪迴之前，我再忍痛報咗另一個3 days tour對鹽湖含淚說再見，因為呢個tour既終點係智利atacama，將會經過鹽湖離開玻利維亞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比起hodaka，brisa既司機更有心，完全無去d奇怪無聊景點，只係停喺無水嘅地方影錯體相，司機仲趴哂地逐個幫我哋影，又拎埋哥斯拉 (佢話係哥斯拉，但分明係暴龍) 同我哋擺pose，影完直接去搵水，仲拎咗架單車出黎比我哋踩! 見我無聊 (文青沈思mode) 仲走過來幫我影咗幾百張相，即刻想比個正評佢呢，親!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p5013577_31704479326_o_zps7mgt7sc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp5013577_31704479326_o_zps7mgt7sc7.jpg&h=1e14cf5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p5013577_31704479326_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp5013577_31704479326_2.jpg&h=d302a76d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p5013577_31704479326_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp5013577_31704479326_3.jpg&h=1fa8a7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示: 最好唔好全身黑去，影出黎d相得返個剪影，色彩又無咁靚。我去果天氣太好了，睇相係好靚，但唔係最靚，最靚係要有雲，好想去多次!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d059d416e53ab345a1584e151bd8fa44a9d5cf","tid":55536,"uid":15714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:25:06.000Z","msg":"好靚，支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de8a88bf37b6a2397ff82745fefe624c25c6cec1","tid":55536,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"留名下年都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8de8eafe213aea20b9356d846fecce7587dcd4","tid":55536,"uid":67931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:20:31.000Z","msg":"正啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd0bb541e2737e63cece6365c86c08fd9b19e60","tid":55536,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/31595203632_aa7a4322fb_z_zpslilaogn1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F31595203632_aa7a4322fb_z_zpslilaogn1.jpg&h=22ac0e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/30900560904_44843dd6e2_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F30900560904_44843dd6e2_z.jpg&h=4cc74767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/P4303351%20Small_zps9gndvdnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2FP4303351%2520Small_zps9gndvdnc.jpg&h=abfcdad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/31704406536_0575e66ae9_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F31704406536_0575e66ae9_z.jpg&h=12fae001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/p4303403_31369098190_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2Fp4303403_31369098190_o.jpg&h=1883fb17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i350.photobucket.com/albums/q414/mountainhk/sa/31626087541_01909af622_z-2_zpszurlgauw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi350.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fq414%2Fmountainhk%2Fsa%2F31626087541_01909af622_z-2_zpszurlgauw.jpg&h=76bf0e44&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}